text: {| |} RFA Airsprite (A115) was a Sprite-class spirits tanker of the Royal Fleet Auxiliary. She was laid up in reserve at Devonport in October 1963, and put up for disposal in January 1965. ==References== Category:Sprite-class tankers Category:Tankers of the Royal Fleet Auxiliary Category:1942 ships
